    "description": "<p>Launched in 1999, our Singapore business has delivered projects across the office, hospitality and leisure, retail and technology, science and health sectors. Our earliest projects led to repeat business and referrals for both local and global blue chip clients, and we quickly established a reputation for high quality delivery. Our projects are self-delivered through our talented in-house specialist team, combining skillsets from construction, engineering, commercial, design management and environmental, health & safety. We care deeply about helping our customers meet their business goals—and our extensive track record, exceptional client list and rate of repeat business prove it.</p>  <p> </p> ",
